description: Dumpling are the gateway to eating around the cart! Explore Chef Mikes fun flavors from around the world with an elvoving menu. Start with his signature dumplings then try his creative burritos punched up with flavors & next his famed grilled fish tacos topped with cilantro slaw. It's more then extraordinary tasting food! We grill for the carnivore, vegan/vegetarian & celiac/gluten free lifestyles!
name: Wandering Chef Catering Cart
